Overview

If you are uncertain which class you belong to, please consult your team captain. In edge cases, the team captain decides where to place the participant fairly. We are happy to give advice to the team captain in case of doubt.

The ETDS committee reserves the right to diverge from the rules stated here to rule in individual cases if conflict should arise.
If a situation arises to which the rules stated here do not (sufficiently) apply, the ETDS committee will decide on the matter. In that case your team captain should contact us.








