If you dance this ClOpen in one discipline (Ballroom or Latin), this does not affect your other discipline.

Assessment by Team Captain
Dancers in fields marked with " * " (e.g. D-Class*) and additionally dancers from equality tournaments generally start with mandatory BlindDating in Breitensport.
Based on experience and performance in previous tournaments, the team captain of the participant's team will choose if the dancer is allowed to start in ClOpen.
The same applies to dancers who have never competed in the desired section (std./lat.) but have reached the highest class in the other.